[ a       <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Axiom> ;
  <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>
          "Entity Regulation Rule 3. The relation 'IL4R, IL2RG, JAK1 in IL4-bound IL4R1:JAK1 are phosphorylated' 'null' 'JAK1 phosphorylates STAT3,STAT6' was inferred because:\n reaction1 has an output that is the enabler of reaction 2." , "Imported from Reactome: https://reactome.org/content/detail/R-HSA-6785807" ;
